{"title":"Limar Ultralight Evo tweaks world’s lightest bike helmet with improved durability","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/15/limar-ultralight-evo-tweaks-worlds-lightest-bike-helmet-with-improved-durability/","date":1626362097000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The new Limar Ultralight Evo road helmet looks almost identical to its lightweight+ predecessor. But it’s hiding some new safety &amp; durability upgrades inside that earn it an evolution name update. While still super light, “<em>The World’s Lightest Helmet</em>” tagline printed on the top of the new Ultralight Evo might not be entirely correct as this generation appears to have added a few extra grams in the name of keeping you safer…</p><h2>Limar Ultralight Evo super lightweight road bike helmet</h2><figure id=\"attachment_265428\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-265428\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb25/ng:webp/ngcb25\" alt=\"Limar Ultralight Evo super lightweight road bike helmet,&nbsp;riding\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-c