rumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105938/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Valentina-Celeste_riding-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-265428\">c. Limar, photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/celestevalentina_cs/\">Valentina Celeste</a></figcaption></figure><p>Limar’s Ultralight road helmet has long fought for the title of “world’s lightest bike helmet”, with us having weighed various iterations from just <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2010/10/13/interbike-2010-limar-introduces-a-lighter-worlds-lighest-helmet-shaves-grams-from-mtb-kids-lids-too/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">159g</a> to <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2011/09/03/limar-updates-ultralight-worlds-lightest-bicycle-helmet-to-make-it-attractive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">173g</a> on our own scales. But now the Ultralight+ gets tweaked, keeping the same overall shape with its distinct spoiler fin, but rethinking its multi-part in-mold construction.</p><h3>What’s new?</h3><figure id=\"attachment_265427\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-265427\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top.jpg\" alt=\"Limar Ultralight Evo super lightweight road bike helmet, top\" width=\"1100\" height=\"700\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-297x189.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-800x509.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-120x76.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-768x489.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-696x443.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-1068x680.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-660x420.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-297x189.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-800x509.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-120x76.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-768x489.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-696x443.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-1068x680.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105933/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_photo-by-Francesca-Caporali_matte-black-top-660x420.jpg 660w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-265427\">photo by Francesca Caporali</figcaption></figure><p>The new Ultralight Evo already employed the most common in-mold construction like almost every modern helmet. And it already used a 2-part shell for more than a decade. But now the lower part of the polycarbonate outer shell extends both higher up and lower down than before.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side.jpg\" alt=\"Limar Ultralight Evo super lightweight road bike helmet,&nbsp;black side\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-297x149.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-800x400.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-120x60.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-768x384.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-696x348.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-1068x534.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-840x420.jpg 840w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb25 src ng ngcb25 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/15105926/Limar-Ultralight-Evo-super-lightweight-road-bike-helmet_matte-black-side-